.row.jumbotron.returning-header
  .col-md-12
    h1 Welcome Back!
.row
  .col-md-12
    h3 Returning Volunteers
    p
      | Having previously volunteered, your personal data is on file. At the end of this
      |  message you will be asked to sign in to your account to review and update your information for 2016.
    h3 Tournament Package
    p
      | There is again a $35.00 fee to volunteer for the 2016 Tournament. For your
      |  investment you will receive a Self Regional Healthcare Foundation Womenâ€™s Health Classic shirt and hat,
      |  complimentary food and beverage during your shift, parking, and a one-day tournament pass.
    h3 Payment
    p
      | Your $35.00 check should be made payable to The Links at Stoney Point Ladies Golf Classic. You
      |  may leave your payment at the Pro Shop or you may mail it to the address shown on the application.
    h3 Terms and Conditions
    p
      | To volunteer on-line, each person must be over 18 years of age and must agree to the terms of the
      |  Waiver for 2016. If not, your information will not be updated and you will not be registered as a 2016 volunteer.
      |  If you are under 18, you may obtain a printed application from your Committee Chair.

.row
- if @attempt > 0
  .alert.alert-danger
    button.close type="button" data-dismiss="alert"
      span aria-hidden="true" &times;
      span.sr-only Close
    h3 Sorry
    | We were unable to match you with a record from previous years. You may take one of two actions:
    ol
      li Check your spelling or the possibility you used a different form of your name and please try again. OR
      li
        | Send us an email
        | &nbsp;
        = mail_to 'stoneypointvolunteer@gmail.com', "here", subject: 'Stoney Point Volunteer  - Help finding my account', body: "I'm a returning volunteer and I've been unable to find my account. Please help me get this sorted out.\n\nHere is my information:\n\nFirst Name: \nLast Name:\nPhone number:\n\nThank you!", class: 'btn btn-default btn-xs'
        |  and submit your information to our helpdesk. You will be contacted by email about a solution.
    h4 Thank you for your patience.

.row.well
  .col-md-6
    = fa_icon "user 4x", class: "text-muted pull-left"
    h4 Login Instructions
    p
      | To login, enter your first name and last name in the spaces provided. Spouses must
      |  login separately.
    .clearfix
  .col-md-6
    = form_tag welcome_volunteers_find_path
      .form-group
        label for="first_name" First Name
        = text_field_tag "search[first_name]", @first_name, class: "form-control", placeholder: 'Enter your first name'
      .form-group
        label for="last_name" Last Name
        = text_field_tag "search[last_name]", @last_name, class: "form-control", placeholder: 'Enter your last name'
      = hidden_field_tag "attempt", @attempt
      = submit_tag :Login, class: 'btn btn-primary pull-right'
    .clearfix
